Solve Wordle puzzles

$ wordle.py --help
Usage: wordle.py [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -l1 TEXT     First letter
  -l2 TEXT     Second letter
  -l3 TEXT     Third letter
  -l4 TEXT     Fourth letter
  -l5 TEXT     Fifth letter
  -p TEXT      Pattern
  -nl1 TEXT    Letters that are not the first letter
  -nl2 TEXT    Letters that are not the second letter
  -nl3 TEXT    Letters that are not the third letter
  -nl4 TEXT    Letters that are not the fourth letter
  -nl5 TEXT    Letters that are not the fifth letter
  -i TEXT      Include words with letters
  -e, -x TEXT  Exclude words with letters
  --help       Show this message and exit.


